"is used as an indicator that the item is invalid, that is that the item "
"cannot be candidate to be displayed in a <_:productname-1/> context menu "
"because some of its informations are missing or erroneous. Here, and though "
"this newly inserted action has some suitable defaults, it lacks a command to"
" be executed to be considered valid by <_:application-2/>"
msgstr ""
"Den nya åtgärden visas också i röd färg i objektlistan. Röd färg används som"
